                  </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>555</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>8#</strong><strong>$a</strong>Original caption cards, arranged by photonegative
                                             number, are available in the Reading Room.
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$b - Availability source</strong> <div class="description">Organizational unit or vendor from which finding aids or other documentation may
                              be obtained.
         </div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
