               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>555</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>0#</strong><strong>$3</strong>Claims settled under Treaty of Washington, May 8, 1871<strong>$a</strong>Preliminary inventory prepared in 1962;<strong>$b</strong>Available in NARS central search room;<strong>$b</strong>NARS Publications Sales Branch;<strong>$d</strong>Ulibarri, George S. ...
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$c - Degree of control</strong> <div class="description">Extent of administrative, bibliographic, or physical control available over the
                              described materials.
         </div>
         <div class="example">
