                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$d - Bibliographic reference</strong> <div class="description">Citation to a published or unpublished index or finding aid to the described
                              materials when it is not cataloged with the item.
         </div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
