                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$3 - Materials specified</strong> <div class="description">Part of the described material to which the field applies.</div>
	  <div class="description">
         <div class="description2"><em>See examples under the descriptions of first indicator value 0 and subfield
                                    $b.</em></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$6 - Linkage</strong> <div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="//www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
